title: Family Guy: The Quest for Stuff hack *fully working update*
description:
Family Guy: The Quest for Stuff hack

updated 23 April fully working now


1) Uninstall prior versions
2) install this file
3) play the game, everything task will give you 4000 clams at a time.
4) send blessings to FlamerFTW



I would recommend, if you have been playing on previous versions, before you uninstall it, create a username/password within the game. Then uninstall it, and login to your new hack with the username to get back your progress. Google+ doesn't work on this hack and facebook sync requires facebook to be uninstalled and reinstalled. so username is the easiest method to keep progress.
